---

<section class="Section Hero u-Clearfix">
    <div class="l-Wrapper">
        <img class="Avatar" src="static/images/avatar.jpg" alt="Arnelle Balane">

        <div>
            <h2 class="Section__Title Hero__Title">Web Developer from <strong>Cebu, Philippines</strong></h2>

            <p class="l-LeftTwoThirds">I love experimenting with and sharing about cool new Web technologies and techniques.</p>
            <p>I'm <strong>@arnellebalane</strong> on
                <span class="SocialIcons">
                    {% externalLink 'Github', 'https://github.com/arnellebalane', ['SocialIcon', 'SocialIcon--github'] %}
                    {% externalLink 'Twitter', 'https://twitter.com/arnellebalane', ['SocialIcon', 'SocialIcon--twitter'] %}
                    {% externalLink 'Dev.to', 'https://dev.to/arnellebalane', ['SocialIcon', 'SocialIcon--devto'] %}
                    {% externalLink 'Instagram', 'https://instagram.com/arnellebalane', ['SocialIcon', 'SocialIcon--instagram'] %}
                    {% externalLink 'LinkedIn', 'https://linkedin.com/in/arnellebalane', ['SocialIcon', 'SocialIcon--linkedin'] %}
                </span>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="Section About">
    <div class="l-Wrapper l-LeftTwoThirds">
        <h1 class="Section__Title">About</h1>

        <p>
            I’m currently a Software Developer at {% externalLink 'Newlogic', 'https://newlogic.io/' %}. Previously, I was the
            Lead Frontend Developer at {% externalLink 'Channelfix', 'https://channelfix.com' %}. I also used to teach a
            Web Engineering class at the University of the Philippines Cebu as a part-time lecturer.
        </p>

        <p>
            On weekends, I’m a co-organizer for {% externalLink 'Google Developers Group Cebu', 'https://gdgcebu.org' %},
            a small team that sets up tech events around the Visayas region. You’ll often find me giving talks and workshops at
            those and other community events.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="Section TalksAndWorkshops">
    <div class="l-Wrapper">
        <img class="TalksAndWorkshops__Image" src="static/images/speaking.jpg" alt="Arnelle Balane">

        <div class="TalksAndWorkshops__Details">
            <h1 class="Section__Title">Talks &amp; Workshops</h1>

            <p>
                I give talks and conduct workshops for community events. I’ve spoken at GDG events, VueJS Cebu, and other meetups,
                usually about Web Platform APIs, Progressive Web Apps, and Firebase.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="UpcomingEvents">
            <h2 class="UpcomingEvents__Label">Upcoming Events</h2>

            {%- for event in events %}
                <article class="Event">
                    <h3 class="Event__Title">{% externalLink event.name, event.url %}</h1>
                    <h4 class="Event__Subtitle">{{ event.description }}</h2>

                    <time class="Event__Date" datetime="2019-05-11">{{ event.date }}</time>
                    <data class="Event__Venue">{{ event.venue }}</data>
                </article>
            {% endfor -%}

            <a class="UpcomingEvents__SeeAll" href="/events">See all talks and workshops</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

